    "The problem selected for this study was, as follows:",
    "In the zoo are a total of 29 lions and water birds, all in perfect condition.",
    "If these have a total of 92 legs, how many of each are there?",
    "In this study, the participants consisted of 58 PSTs who were enrolled in a mathematics education course.",
    "The course originally had 59 PSTs enrolled."
  ]
}